Phosphopantothenoylcysteine decarboxylase (EC 4.1.1.36) (Halotolerance
protein Hal3a) (AtHal3a) (PPCDC) (AtCoaC).
"Arabidopsis thaliana AtHAL3: a flavoprotein related to salt and
osmotic tolerance and plant growth.";
