"Large-scale analysis of RIKEN Arabidopsis full-length (RAFL) cDNAs.";
"Arabidopsis thaliana flavoprotein AtHAL3a catalyzes the
decarboxylation of 4'-Phosphopantothenoylcysteine to 4'-
phosphopantetheine, a key step in coenzyme A biosynthesis.";
"Molecular characterization of the Arabidopsis thaliana flavoprotein
AtHAL3a reveals the general reaction mechanism of 4'-
